'<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/computer-laptop-repairs/\">COMPUTER &amp; LAPTOP REPAIRS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWhether you have a software or hardware problem e-tec Computer Services can repair any make of computer or laptop.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/computer-laptop-repairs/\">Computer &amp; Laptop Repairs &gt;&gt;</a>'),(379,5,'_service_text_two','field_578f8d2690de1'),(380,5,'service_icon_three','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/upgrades/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-90\" title=\"Upgrades\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/upgrades-icon.png\" alt=\"Upgrades icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(381,5,'_service_icon_three','field_578f8d6290de2'),(382,5,'service_text_three','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/upgrades/\">UPGRADES</a></strong>\r\n\r\nBefore you decide to buy a new computer or laptop to replace your sluggish one, why not save some money and give it a new lease of life with an upgrade.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/upgrades\">Upgrade services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(383,5,'_service_text_three','field_578f8d7890de3'),(384,5,'service_icon_four','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-85\" title=\"New PCs &amp; Laptops\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/new-pcs-laptops-icon.png\" alt=\"New PCs &amp; Laptops icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(385,5,'_service_icon_four','field_578f8d8f90de4'),(386,5,'service_text_four','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops/\">NEW PCS &amp; LAPTOPS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWe can provide new workstations and laptops that are perfect for business use and custom built PC’s that are suitable for business and pleasure.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops\">New PC\'s &amp; Laptops &gt;&gt;</a>'),(387,5,'_service_text_four','field_578f8da590de5'),(388,5,'service_icon_five','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/tune-ups/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-89\" title=\"Tune-Ups\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/tune-ups-icon.png\" alt=\"Tune-Ups icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(389,5,'_service_icon_five','field_578f8dbc90de6'),(390,5,'service_text_five','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/tune-ups/\">TUNE-UPS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nOver time your computer can start to slow down, become unresponsive and reliable. A computer tune-up service can make your computer run like new.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/tune-ups\">Tune-Up services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(391,5,'_service_text_five','field_578f8dc990de7'),(392,5,'service_icon_six','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-84\" title=\"Network\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/network-icon.png\" alt=\"Network icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(393,5,'_service_icon_six','field_578f8dd990de8'),(394,5,'service_text_six','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network/\">NETWORK</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re working in an office, working from home or just general day-to-day family use, it’s important to have the correct network setup for your needs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network\">Network services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(395,5,'_service_text_six','field_578f8de990de9'),(396,5,'service_icon_seven','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-83\" title=\"Data\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/data-icon.png\" alt=\"Data icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(397,5,'_service_icon_seven','field_578f8e1f90dea'),(398,5,'service_text_seven','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data/\">DATA</a></strong>\r\n\r\nThe importance of data in today’s society is more important than ever. We all have several devices that use data and store personal information about us.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data\">Data solutions &gt;&gt;</a>'),(399,5,'_service_text_seven','field_578f8e2e90deb'),(400,5,'service_icon_eight','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-86\" title=\"Refurbi