_seven','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/data/\">DATA</a></strong>\r\n\r\nThe importance of data in today’s society is more important than ever. We all have several devices that use data and store personal information about us.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data\">Data solutions &gt;&gt;</a>'),(2711,221,'_service_text_seven','field_578f8e2e90deb'),(2712,221,'service_icon_eight','<a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-86\" title=\"Refurbished PCs\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/refurbished-pcs.png\" alt=\"Refurbished PCs icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(2713,221,'_service_icon_eight','field_578f8e3c90dec'),(2714,221,'service_text_eight','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\">REFURBISHED PCS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a high spec PC or laptop and want to save money, then consider a refurbished PC or laptop from e-tec Computer Services.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs\">Refurbished PC\'s &gt;&gt;</a>'),(2715,221,'_service_text_eight','field_578f8e4d90ded'),(2767,244,'_wp_attached_file','2017/01/abc-blue.png'),(2768,244,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:80;s:6:\"height\";i:60;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2017/01/abc-blue.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:0:{}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(2769,245,'_wp_attached_file','2017/01/cyber-pulse-logo.png'),(2770,245,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:231;s:6:\"height\";i:60;s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"2017/01/cyber-pulse-logo.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"cyber-pulse-logo-100x60.png\";s:5: