 /> No fix - no fee   <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/check.gif\" alt=\"check\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" /> Fast response   <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/check.gif\" alt=\"check\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" /> Fixed fee - No hidden charges'),(3178,952,'_check','field_586f77d089c60'),(3179,952,'service_title','How we can help'),(3180,952,'_service_title','field_578f8c3d90ddd'),(3181,952,'service_icon_one','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/support/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-88 size-thumbnail\" title=\"Support\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/support-icon.png\" alt=\"Support icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3182,952,'_service_icon_one','field_578f8cc790dde'),(3183,952,'service_text_one','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/it-support/\">IT SUPPORT</a></strong>\r\n\r\nIf your business relies on a network or computers for daily activities, then you need to ensure that everything is working as it should to reduce downtime.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/it-support\">IT Support services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3184,952,'_service_text_one','field_578f8cf990ddf'),(3185,952,'service_icon_two','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/repairs/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-87\" title=\"Repairs\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/repair-icon.png\" alt=\"Repair icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3186,952,'_service_icon_two','field_578f8d1590de0'),(3187,952,'service_text_two','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/computer-laptop-repairs/\">COMPUTER &amp; LAPTOP REPAIRS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWhether you have a software or hardware problem e-tec Computer Services can repair any make of computer or laptop.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/computer-laptop-repairs\">Computer &amp; Laptop Repairs &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3188,952,'_service_text_two','field_578f8d2690de1'),(3189,952,'service_icon_three','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/upgrades/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-90\" title=\"Upgrades\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/upgrades-icon.png\" alt=\"Upgrades icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3190,952,'_service_icon_three','field_578f8d6290de2'),(3191,952,'service_text_three','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/upgrades/\">UPGRADES</a></strong>\r\n\r\nBefore you decide to buy a new computer or laptop to replace your sluggish one, why not save some money and give it a new lease of life with an upgrade.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/upgrades\">Upgrade services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3192,952,'_service_text_three','field_578f8d7890de3'),(3193,952,'service_icon_four','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-85\" title=\"New PCs &amp; Laptops\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/new-pcs-laptops-icon.png\" alt=\"New PCs &amp; Laptops icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3194,952,'_service_icon_four','field_578f8d8f90de4'),(3195,952,'service_text_four','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops/\">NEW PCS &amp; LAPTOPS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWe can provide new workstations and laptops that are perfect for business use and custom built PC’s that are suitable for business and pleasure.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/new-pcs-laptops\">New PC\'s &amp; Laptops &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3196,952,'_service_text_four','field_578f8da590de5'),(3197,952,'service_icon_five','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/tune-ups/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-89\" title=\"Tune-Ups\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/tune-ups-icon.png\" alt=\"Tune-Ups icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3198,952,'_service_icon_five','field_578f8dbc90de6'),(3199,952,'service_text_five','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/tune-ups/\">TUNE-UPS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nOver time your computer can start to slow down, become unresponsive and reliable. A computer tune-up service can make your computer run like new.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/tune-ups\">Tune-Up services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3200,952,'_service_text_five','field_578f8dc990de7'),(3201,952,'service_icon_six','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-84\" title=\"Network\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/network-icon.png\" alt=\"Network icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3202,952,'_service_icon_six','field_578f8dd990de8'),(3203,952,'service_text_six','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/network/\">NETWORK</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re working in an office, working from home or just general day-to-day family use, it’s important to have the correct network setup for your needs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network\">Network services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3204,952,'_service_text_six','field_578f8de990de9'),(3205,952,'service_icon_seven','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-83\" title=\"Data\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/data-icon.png\" alt=\"Data icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3206,952,'_service_icon_seven','field_578f8e1f90dea'),(3207,952,'service_text_seven','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/data/\">DATA</a></strong>\r\n\r\nThe importance of data in today’s society is more important than ever. We all have several devices that use data and store personal information about us.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data\">Data solutions &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3208,952,'_service_text_seven','field_578f8e2e90deb'),(3209,952,'service_icon_eight','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-86\" title=\"Refurbished PCs\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/refurbished-pcs.png\" alt=\"Refurbished PCs icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3210,952,'_service_icon_eight','field_578f8e3c90dec'),(3211,952,'service_text_eight','<strong><a href=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs