guidelines. That is where it should be eye-catching.\nWe can redesign your website responsive by writing the back-end code with HTML5 and CSS3 technologies with which your site will auto-fit according to the devices.\nLet me know if I should share a customized plan as per your website requirement.\nI am looking forward to your kind response.\nRegards\n Kitona Black\n Skype Us: live:softminders\n Call Us: +1 (925) 297-5855 (Available on Whatsapp)\n 00917439740725\n Soft Minders Pvt Ltd.'),(3762,1015,'_form_id','1'),(3763,1015,'_seq_num','36'),(3764,1016,'_field_1','Moti Singh'),(3765,1016,'_field_2','info@ranksindia.com'),(3766,1016,'_field_5','9650460670'),(3767,1016,'_field_3','Hi,\n\nDo you want more clients and customers?\n\nWe will help you by placing your website on the 1st page on Google.\n\nI will be happy to send the Free Proposal and Pricing.\n\nWant to know more about my company, costing on SEO, results etc.\n\nPlease email us for full proposal.\n\nThank You!\nMoti | Ranks Digital Media\nWhatsAPP: +91 9650460670\n'),(3768,1016,'_form_id','1'),(3769,1016,'_seq_num','37'),(3770,1018,'message','CONTACT'),(3771,1018,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3772,1019,'message','CONTACT'),(3773,1019,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3774,1020,'message','Everything from IT support to product repair'),(3775,1020,'_message','field_578f8bcb90ddb'),(3776,1020,'urgent','For urgent computer and laptop repairs, call 07977 697 099'),(3777,1020,'_urgent','field_578f8be390ddc'),(3778,1020,'check','<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/check.gif\" alt=\"check\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" /> No call-out charge    <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/check.gif\" alt=\"check\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" /> No fix - no fee   <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/check.gif\" alt=\"check\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" /> Fast response   <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-193\" src=\"/wp-c