 office, working from home or just general day-to-day family use, it’s important to have the correct network setup for your needs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/network\">Network services &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3889,1024,'_service_text_six','field_578f8de990de9'),(3890,1024,'service_icon_seven','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-83\" title=\"Data\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/data-icon.png\" alt=\"Data icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3891,1024,'_service_icon_seven','field_578f8e1f90dea'),(3892,1024,'service_text_seven','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data/\">DATA</a></strong>\r\n\r\nThe importance of data in today’s society is more important than ever. We all have several devices that use data and store personal information about us.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/data\">Data solutions &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3893,1024,'_service_text_seven','field_578f8e2e90deb'),(3894,1024,'service_icon_eight','<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\"><img class=\"img-responsive alignnone wp-image-86\" title=\"Refurbished PCs\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/refurbished-pcs.png\" alt=\"Refurbished PCs icon\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></a>'),(3895,1024,'_service_icon_eight','field_578f8e3c90dec'),(3896,1024,'service_text_eight','<strong><a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs/\">REFURBISHED PCS</a></strong>\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a high spec PC or laptop and want to save money, then consider a refurbished PC or laptop from e-tec Computer Services.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/how-we-can-help/refurbished-pcs\">Refurbished PC\'s &gt;&gt;</a>'),(3897,1024,'_service_text_eight','field_578f8e4d90ded'),(3898,1025,'message','IT SUPPORT'),(3899,1025,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3900,1026,'message','UPGRADES'),(3901,1026,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3902,1027,'message','NEW PCS & LAPTOPS'),(3903,1027,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3904,1028,'message','TUNE-UPS'),(3905,1028,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3906,1029,'message','NETWORK'),(3907,1029,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3908,1030,'message','DATA'),(3909,1030,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3910,1031,'message','REFURBISHED PCS'),(3911,1031,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3912,1032,'message','WHO ARE WE'),(3913,1032,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3914,1034,'message','PRIVACY & COOKIE POLICY'),(3915,1034,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3982,1054,'_field_1','Enzo'),(3983,1054,'_field_2','enzo@e-tecpc.co.uk'),(3984,1054,'_field_5','123456789'),(3985,1054,'_field_3','TEST'),(3986,1054,'_form_id','1'),(3987,1054,'_seq_num','3'),(3988,1055,'message','CONTACT'),(3989,1055,'_message','field_5795f58aa0347'),(3990,1056,'_field_1','qwert'),(3991,1056,'_field_2','enzo@e-tecpc.co.uk'),(3992,1056,'_field_5',''),(3993,1056,'_field_3','test'),(3994,1056,'_form_id','1'),(3995,1056,'_seq_num','4'),(3996,1057,'_field_1','tim'),(3997,1057,'_field_2','tim@subserve.co.uk'),(3998,1057,'_field_5','+441216303773'),(3999,1057,'_field_3','hi\ni found you in yellow page.\ni m reseller\nsome time my customer demand\'s me refurbish items.\nyou have a stock refurbish or used items like hard disk router\'s switch motherboard\'s. lot of computer related items.\nSo you have some stock please tell me \nmy b i have order\nor i tell you part number you find for me \nthanks\' '),(4000,1057,'_form_id','1'),(4001,1057,'_seq_num','5'),(4002,1058,'_field_1','Andy Taylor'),(4003,1058,'_field_2','andytaylor.gsxr@sky.com'),(4004,1058,'_field_5',''),(4005,1058,'_field_3','I have a Samsung RV511 with an i5 intel core currently running Win 7.  I had restored to factory and spent the last couple of weeks updating the Win 7 version it restored itself to to get it something like the pre-restored version of Win 7  (this has not been fun as you will aware the support for Win 7 ended a couple of years ago).  This was in the hope of upgrading to Win 10.  I have a license key for Win 10 Pro but it will not upgrade.  I can download Win 10 but I get the dreaded Blue Windows symbol and a OS_Safe boot type of message.\nI would like a quote to get Win 10 installed onto the laptop (if practical as it\'s an old laptop)  I use it for basic functions, emails, iTunes and Microsoft Office (which I have access to Office 365 from work) for word PP etc.\nIt\'s never going to be a gaming laptop but I do need it to access my hard drives (separate items) with photos and videos on.\nIf you can provide a quote and/or advice as to the best course of action it would be apprciated\nCheers in advance'),(4006,1058,'_form_id','1'),(4007,1058,'_seq_num','6'),(4008,1059,'_field_1','n nero'),(4009,1059,'_field_2','natalie.nero@tameside.gov.uk'),(4010,1059,'_field_5',''),(4011,1059,'_field_3','Good afternoon\n\nCould you please advise if you have any current vacancies for people looking to work within the repair sector.  I work within the Tameside in Work team at Tameside Council and I have a client that is currently in work but looking to go into repairing computers as this is his passion.\n\nAny information would be appreciated.\n\nKind regard\nNatalie\n'),(4012,1059,'_form_id','1'),(4013,1059,'_seq_num','7'),(4014,1060,'_field_1','Yossi Katsavi'),(4015,1060,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4016,1060,'_field_5','+1 631 601-0233'),(4017,1060,'_field_3','I am contacting you on behalf of Emsisoft (www.emsisoft.com) for checking your interest in reselling Emsisoft anti virus/malware/ransomware solutions.\n\nEmsisoft protects a few million windows endpoints worldwide. Emsisoft is a lightweight solution with remote/cloud management features.\n\nWe are looking for computer sales and services companies, which will resell Emsisoft.\n\nPlease get back to me for more information, if you are interested.'),(4018,1060,'_form_id','1'),(4019,1060,'_seq_num','8'),(4020,1061,'_field_1','Amy Bartlett'),(4021,1061,'_field_2','amybartlett.seomarketing@gmail.com'),(4022,1061,'_field_5','02922747444'),(4023,1061,'_field_3','\"Hi, \n\nMy name is Amy and I’m a performance marketing specialist here in the UK. We’ve carried out some initial research on your website/sector and I noticed that your online visibility on search engines is lower than average for your sector. \n\nWith your permission I’d like to send you a free report showing you a few things you can do on your own (without needing to hire anyone) to greatly improve these search results for you. The report is very detailed and comes with its own detailed instructions. It will show you exactly what needs to be addressed to move you up in the rankings dramatically. \n\nWould that be, okay? Again, this is completely free- no costs whatsoever just our way of making a super strong first impression as experts in E-Commerce marketing!  \n\nPlease email us back for a free report.\n\n\nWarm Regards,\nAmy Bartlett\namybartlett.seomarketing@gmail.com\nMarketing Account Manager\n\n\n\nIf you’re NOT interested, simply reply “NO” and I will not contact you again.\"\n'),(4024,1061,'_form_id','1'),(4025,1061,'_seq_num','9'),(4026,1062,'_field_1','Yossi Katsavi'),(4027,1062,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4028,1062,'_field_5','+1 631 601-0233'),(4029,1062,'_field_3','I am contacting you on behalf of Dade2 (www.dade2.net) , a UK based provider of cloud servers with worldwide data centers.\n\nCompared with the competition (AWS, Azure) Dade2 offers a 30% to 50% cost advantage for the same performance level.\n\nWe are looking for IT service providers, which will offer and resell Dade2 servers to their customers \n\nPlease get back to me for more information, if you will be interested in evaluating the partnership opportunity.'),(4030,1062,'_form_id','1'),(4031,1062,'_seq_num','10'),(4032,1063,'_field_1','Helen Waters'),(4033,1063,'_field_2','helen.marketingagencyuk@gmail.com'),(4034,1063,'_field_5','02922747447'),(4035,1063,'_field_3','\"Hi,\n\nHow would you like to get a lot more clients through the website over the Xmas season?\n\nMy name is Helen and I’m a performance marketing specialist here in the UK. We’ve carried out some initial research on your website/sector and I noticed that your online visibility on search engines is lower than average for your sector.\n\nWith your permission I’d like to send you a free report showing you a few things you can do on your own (without needing to hire anyone) to greatly improve these search results for you. The report is very detailed and comes with its own detailed instructions. It will show you how you can actually increase leads &amp; sales through your website. So that your website reaches the rank that you deserve.\n\nWould that be, okay? Again, this is completely free- no costs whatsoever just our way of making a super strong first impression as experts in E-Commerce marketing!\n\nPlease email us back for a free report.\n\n\nWarm Regards,\nHelen Waters\nhelen.marketingagencyuk@gmail.com\nMarketing Account Manager\n\n\n\n\nIf you’re NOT interested, simply reply “NO” and I will not contact you again.\"\n'),(4036,1063,'_form_id','1'),(4037,1063,'_seq_num','11'),(4038,1064,'_field_1','ROY SILVER'),(4039,1064,'_field_2','rsilver1966@btinternet.com'),(4040,1064,'_field_5','01457832833'),(4041,1064,'_field_3','hi \ni have a lenovo p360 and i need the ram upgrading from 237gb and  more storage on disk c to take about  6 tb \nas im swapping from a ideacenter which has 1.8tb on disc c  \nalso if possilbe can you get rid of the microsoft edge  and install google chrome ive tried swapping but it reverts back to microsoft \ni have recently purchased the p360 from a dealer in london and i dont want to send it back to them as i live in mossley \ni can gladley drop the unit off to you\nregards \nROY '),(4042,1064,'_form_id','1'),(4043,1064,'_seq_num','12'),(4044,1065,'_field_1','Andrew Fitzpatrick'),(4045,1065,'_field_2','andrew.fitzpatrick@gla-ac-edu.org'),(4046,1065,'_field_5',''),(4047,1065,'_field_3','We would need you to advise us with pricing and availability for the product listed below.\n\nSanDisk Professional G-Drive SSD 1TB.\n\nKind Regards\n\nAndrew Fitzpatrick\nProcurement Director\nTel 44 (0) 141 530 3507\n\nProcurement Office (Tay House)\nUniversity of Glasgow\nUniversity Ave,\nGlasgow G12 8QQ\nUnited Kingdom\nVAT number GB 671798093\ncompany reg: SC004401'),(4048,1065,'_form_id','1'),(4049,1065,'_seq_num','13'),(4050,1066,'_field_1','Helen Waters'),(4051,1066,'_field_2','helen.marketingagencyuk@gmail.com'),(4052,1066,'_field_5','02922747447'),(4053,1066,'_field_3','\"Hi,\n\nMy name is Helen and I’m a performance marketing specialist here in the UK. We’ve carried out some initial research on your website/sector and I noticed that your online visibility on search engines is lower than average for your sector.\n\nWith your permission I’d like to send you a free report showing you a few things you can do on your own (without needing to hire anyone) to greatly improve these search results for you. The report is comprehensive and comes with its own detailed instructions. It will show you how you can actually increase leads &amp; sales through your website. We’d be more than happy to even walk you through the report.\n\nWould that be, okay? Again, this is completely free- no costs whatsoever just our way of making a super strong first impression as experts in E-Commerce marketing!\n\nPlease email us back for a free report.\n\n\nWarm Regards,\nHelen Waters\nhelen.marketingagencyuk@gmail.com\nMarketing Account Manager\n\n\n\nIf you’re NOT interested, simply reply “NO” and I will not contact you again.\"\n'),(4054,1066,'_form_id','1'),(4055,1066,'_seq_num','14'),(4058,1070,'_field_1','Rainie'),(4059,1070,'_field_2','rainie@ivostech.com'),(4060,1070,'_field_5','3145933005'),(4061,1070,'_field_3','Hi Dear,\nThis is Rainie  from Chinese Manufacturer. We mainly sell laptop parts .\nAll in stock！The website has many products you can click and watch.\nPls view if you are interested in. \nHere are some LCD display just for your reference:\n14.0\" 30Pin HD Top/Bottom Tabs non touch\nNT140WHM-N41            $32.00 \n14.0\" 30Pin FHD Top/Bottom Tabs non touch             \nB140HAN01.3                 $49.00\n14.0\" 30Pin FHD No Tabs non touch (Glossy)          \nN140HGA-EA1                $49.00\n14.0\" 40Pin FHD Top/Bottom Tabs touch (Digitizer Glossy）\nB140HAK02.2                  $78.50\n14.0\" 40Pin FHD No Tabs touch (Digitizer Glossy）\nB140HAK02.4                  $57.50\n---------------------------\nRainie Lin\nsales Manger | IVOS Tech\nEmail: rainie@ivostech.com\nWhats App:+86 13145933005\nWeb: www.ivostech.com'),(4062,1070,'_form_id','1'),(4063,1070,'_seq_num','15'),(4064,1071,'_field_1','Rainie'),(4065,1071,'_field_2','rainie@ivostech.com'),(4066,1071,'_field_5','3145933005'),(4067,1071,'_field_3','Hi Dear,\nThis is Rainie  from Chinese Manufacturer. We mainly sell laptop parts .\nAll in stock！The website has many products you can click and watch.\nPls view if you are interested in. \nHere are some LCD display just for your reference:\n14.0\" 30Pin HD Top/Bottom Tabs non touch\nNT140WHM-N41            $32.00 \n14.0\" 30Pin FHD Top/Bottom Tabs non touch             \nB140HAN01.3                 $49.00\n14.0\" 30Pin FHD No Tabs non touch (Glossy)          \nN140HGA-EA1                $49.00\n14.0\" 40Pin FHD Top/Bottom Tabs touch (Digitizer Glossy）\nB140HAK02.2                  $78.50\n14.0\" 40Pin FHD No Tabs touch (Digitizer Glossy）\nB140HAK02.4                  $57.50\n---------------------------\nRainie Lin\nsales Manger | IVOS Tech\nEmail: rainie@ivostech.com\nWhats App:+86 13145933005\nWeb: www.ivostech.com'),(4068,1071,'_form_id','1'),(4069,1071,'_seq_num','15'),(4070,1072,'_field_1','Yossi Katsavi'),(4071,1072,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4072,1072,'_field_5','+1 631 601-0233'),(4073,1072,'_field_3','(Please forward to the person in charge of evaluating new products for reselling at E-Tec Computer Services)\n\nI am getting in contact with you on behalf of FileHold (www.filehold.com) regarding partnership. \n\nFileHold is a Canadian company developing document management software\n\nWe are looking for IT service providers, which will resell FileHold DMS system to their customers.\n\nThe solution is suitable for medium sized companies are large organizations. FileHold provides comparable functionality to enterprise-grade DMS systems at a lower cost.\n\nPlease get back to me, if you are interested in exploring the partnership opportunity.'),(4074,1072,'_form_id','1'),(4075,1072,'_seq_num','15'),(4076,1073,'_field_1','Jacob Black'),(4077,1073,'_field_2','jacob@wikimastery.net'),(4078,1073,'_field_5','8149805065'),(4079,1073,'_field_3','\nWikipedia is considered to be the World’s most significant tool for reference material. The Wiki links show up on the 1st page of Google 97% of the time. With a Page on one of the most revered reference tools, you are sure to get yourself or your business noticed. So if you\'re thinking of getting a Wikipedia Page created, it\'s the best time of the year.\n\nIf you are interested in getting more information just respond back to this email.\n\nThanks,\n\nJacob Black\nWiki Mastery\njacob@wikimastery.net\n\nRespond with stop to optout.'),(4080,1073,'_form_id','1'),(4081,1073,'_seq_num','15'),(4082,1074,'_field_1','Dipesh Lunthi'),(4083,1074,'_field_2','Webrank04@gmail.com'),(4084,1074,'_field_5','7077060205'),(4085,1074,'_field_3','⁠Hello\n\nWarm greetings!\n\nI wanted to quickly reach out and offer you an audit I completed for your website. This audit points out the actual issues on the site that are stopping you from dominating Google Search rankings and generate more business.\n\nI will be happy to share this audit with you via email if you are happy to review it. Please let me know if you want me to send it over and if you think it’s worth then we can talk about the solutions.\n\nLooking forward to hear from you with your email address and contact details.\n\nThanks,\nDipesh Lunthi'),(4086,1074,'_form_id','1'),(4087,1074,'_seq_num','15'),(4088,1075,'_field_1','Matt Carner'),(4089,1075,'_field_2','mattseocarner@gmail.com'),(4090,1075,'_field_5','2356895054'),(4091,1075,'_field_3','Re: SEO Report\n\nHello\n\nI was checking your website and see you have a good design and it looks great, but it\'s not ranking on Google and other major search engines.\n\nWith your permission : I would like to send you a SEO report with prices showing you a few things to greatly improve these search results for you. These things are not difficult, and my report will be very specific. It will show you exactly what needs to be done to move you up in the rankings dramatically.\n\nKindly let me know if you would be interested so we can email you more details or schedule a call.\n\nThank you\nMatt Carner\n\n'),(4092,1075,'_form_id','1'),(4093,1075,'_seq_num','15'),(4094,1076,'_field_1','Anna Liu'),(4095,1076,'_field_2','Anna@ivostech.com'),(4096,1076,'_field_5','+86 15527346727'),(4097,1076,'_field_3','Hello,\n\nWe are a laptop repair parts supplier from China.We mainly sell LCD Covers,LCD Screens,Keyboards,Batteries,Adapters,Motherboards and other small items.We are looking for some cooperation and just to see if any chance we can be your supplier.\nPlease do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or concerns.\n\nThanks and Best Regards,\n'),(4098,1076,'_form_id','1'),(4099,1076,'_seq_num','15'),(4100,1077,'_field_1','Shirish Agarwal'),(4101,1077,'_field_2','shirish@flow20digitalmarketing.co.uk'),(4102,1077,'_field_5','07947512314'),(4103,1077,'_field_3','Hi there\n\nI was wondering if it would be possible to schedule a meeting or a phone chat with someone who looks after the business development side of things?\n\nI have over 12 years of experience generating leads via SEO and PPC for technology and IT businesses and just wondered if you needed any help in this area from someone who has a very good working knowledge of your industry.\n\nBut first, to establish some credibility(!):\n\n- You will find my own website on page 1 for website marketing London, SEO company Brixton, PPC agency Shoreditch, LinkedIn ads agency London and many more\n- I also have featured snippet visibility for searches such as \"SEO techniques to avoid” and “can you do SEO without a website\" to name a few (and, I can get your website featured within the featured snippets, too!)\n- I was featured in a top 30 digital marketers to follow in 2017 and 2019 - https://www.relevance.com/top-25-digital-marketing-influencers-to-follow-in-2017/\n\nMy rates (ex. VAT)\nSEO from £1250 per month. \nPPC from £550 per month.\n \nI can also offer a performance based SEO where I tie part of my charges to results.\n\nIf it\'s easier, please feel free to book a time for a chat directly on my calendar here https://calendly.com/shirishaga/\n\nThank you very much.\nShirish'),(4104,1077,'_form_id','1'),(4105,1077,'_seq_num','15'),(4106,1078,'_field_1','Sean Somers'),(4107,1078,'_field_2','sean.somers@tameside.ac.uk'),(4108,1078,'_field_5','01619086798'),(4109,1078,'_field_3','Hi,\n\nMy name is Sean and I am part of the Employability team at Tameside and Clarendon Sixth Form College. I help to set up Work Placement opportunities for our learners which is an element of their programme of study.\n\nI have a cohort of Digital learners, who are studying at Level 3, and they are eager to put their classroom learning into real-world practice. I have placed learners this year in local businesses, High schools, Primary schools, Hospitals and local councils, assisting in the IT departments, or helping the person(s) responsible for digital activities i.e., websites, social media, vlogging and administration.\nThey have a lot to offer, and their natural knowledge of IT coupled with their course content make them an asset. \n\nI am looking for partnerships with employers in Tameside and Greater Manchester, especially those that have a strong online presence and are interested in the next generation of digitally skilled workers.\n\nIf you feel like this is something you can support, I\'d be delighted to talk some more.\n\n'),(4110,1078,'_form_id','1'),(4111,1078,'_seq_num','15'),(4112,1079,'_field_1','Kevin Balor'),(4113,1079,'_field_2','kevin@wikiexpertinc.net'),(4114,1079,'_field_5','8149805065'),(4115,1079,'_field_3','Wikipedia is considered to be the World’s most significant tool for reference material. The Wiki links show up on the 1st page of Google 97% of the time. With a Page on one of the most revered reference tools, you are sure to get yourself or your business noticed. So if you\'re thinking of getting a Wikipedia Page created, it\'s the best time of the year.\n\nIf you are interested in getting more information just respond back to this email.\n\nThanks,\n\nKevin Balor\nWiki Experts Inc\nkevin@wikiexpertinc.net\n\nRespond with stop to optout.'),(4116,1079,'_form_id','1'),(4117,1079,'_seq_num','15'),(4118,1080,'_field_1','Yossi Katsavi'),(4119,1080,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4120,1080,'_field_5','+1 631 601-0233'),(4121,1080,'_field_3','I am contacting you on behalf of ShieldApps regarding a possible partnership.\n\nShieldApps (www.shieldapps.com) is a suite of cyber-security software solutions for preventing identity-theft and protecting the privacy of internet users.\n\nWe are looking for computer repair  companies that will resell ShieldApps solutions to their residential customers under their own brand (white-label) \n\nWith this partnership you will be generating additional revenues,  while protecting the identity and privacy of your customers.\n\nPlease get back to me for more information, if you wish to explore a possible partnership.'),(4122,1080,'_form_id','1'),(4123,1080,'_seq_num','15'),(4124,1081,'_field_1','Damian'),(4125,1081,'_field_2','dragonek.gram@gmail.com'),(4126,1081,'_field_5',''),(4127,1081,'_field_3','Hi, I was just wondering how much will it cost to replace my Acer Nitro 5 (AN515-42-R55Z) screen. Should I order the screen or u going to order it?'),(4128,1081,'_form_id','1'),(4129,1081,'_seq_num','15'),(4130,1082,'_field_1','Anita'),(4131,1082,'_field_2','develop01@rogantech.com'),(4132,1082,'_field_5','0086-15302651054'),(4133,1082,'_field_3','Good day, we are broker specialized in IT product and parts which is hard-to-find with more than 20 years experience.\n\nDo you have any inquiry of computer parts or server parts please? \n\nWaiting for your response.\n\nKind regards\nAnita | Sales Development\n\nRogan Tech Limited\n \nE-mail: develop01@rogantech.com\nMob/WeChat: +86-15302651054\nWhatsApp: +86-15302651054\nWebsite: www.rogantech.com\n'),(4134,1082,'_form_id','1'),(4135,1082,'_seq_num','15'),(4136,1083,'_field_1','Yossi Katsavi'),(4137,1083,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4138,1083,'_field_5','+1 631 601-0233'),(4139,1083,'_field_3','I am contacting you on behalf of Yonetim Academy (https://www.awsegitimi.com/en/) regarding possible collaboration.\n\nYonetim Academy is a high-ranking training provider accredited by AWS for delivering official AWS courses \n \nWe are looking for IT service providers which will resell the AWS courses to their suitable clients.\n\nThe target clients are enterprises using the AWS cloud infrastructure with internal IT support team.\n\nUp to now Yonetim Academy has provided the courses to 120 clients in 30 countries.\n\nThe training courses can be delivered online or on-site.\n\nPlease let me know if you have such customers and if you wish to evaluate this partnership opportunity.'),(4140,1083,'_form_id','1'),(4141,1083,'_seq_num','15'),(4142,1084,'_field_1','Tom'),(4143,1084,'_field_2','tomo.hay@gmail.com'),(4144,1084,'_field_5',''),(4145,1084,'_field_3','I have an Alienware 15 R3 - The laptop only works on AC power, we originally thought the battery was dead but have had it replaced twice with no luck. I believe it is likely the connector or something along those lines that needs replacing.\n\nIs this something you can fix?\n\nThanks'),(4146,1084,'_form_id','1'),(4147,1084,'_seq_num','15'),(4148,1085,'_field_1','Dipesh Lunthi'),(4149,1085,'_field_2','Seorankings001@gmail.com'),(4150,1085,'_field_5','7077060205'),(4151,1085,'_field_3','\"Hello and Good Day!\n\nI\'m Dipesh Lunthi, Business Development Manager at a reputable online marketing company based in India. I noticed that your website is not ranking well on Google and other search engines, which could be affecting your visibility to potential customers.\n\nWhile your website design is impressive, it\'s crucial to enhance its visibility on search engines to attract more traffic. Our 360° Digital Marketing Agency, backed by experienced and innovative SEO Experts, has a proven track record of helping over 1000+ businesses achieve top rankings on Google\'s first page.\n\nWe specialize in providing cost-effective and high-quality solutions to small and medium-sized companies like yours. Our tailored strategies are designed to optimize your online presence and capture the attention of your target audience.\n\nTo improve your website\'s visibility on search engines and maximize your chances of reaching potential customers, I would be happy to send you a detailed proposal, price list, and compelling case studies.\n\nLet\'s elevate your online presence to new heights!\n\nThanks,\nDipesh Lunthi\"\n'),(4152,1085,'_form_id','1'),(4153,1085,'_seq_num','15'),(4154,1086,'_field_1','Alfie Carter'),(4155,1086,'_field_2','ideas@createprogressai.co.uk'),(4156,1086,'_field_5','02081500294'),(4157,1086,'_field_3','Hi there\n\nAlfie here, from CreateProgress.ai.\n\nI’m an AI consultant specialising in helping businesses become more productive and efficient by helping them leverage the incredible power of AI.\n\nHere are some ways I can help you implement AI in your business:\n \n- Client onboarding using AI chatbots\n- Automate screening of resumes and other HR tasks\n- Background research and drafting of documents\n- Analyse your sales meetings using AI transcription and analytics\n- Automation of your marketing campaigns\n \nI will be happy to have a chat and tell you specific ways on how you can implement AI to improve profitability, reduce overheads and gain a competitive advantage.\n\nBook your free consultation call with me here - https://calendly.com/d/ckbx-3jv-97x/create-progress-discovery-call\n\nOr, feel free to respond to this message and I will be happy to answer any other questions you may have.\n\nThanks\nAlfie Carter\nhttps://CreateProgress.ai'),(4158,1086,'_form_id','1'),(4159,1086,'_seq_num','15'),(4160,1087,'_field_1','Hannah'),(4161,1087,'_field_2','hrbooth80@gmail.com'),(4162,1087,'_field_5','07305559415'),(4163,1087,'_field_3','Hi my HP Envy 360x Laptop has a broken cooling fan and I was wondering if you were able to repair/replace the fan? Please can I be contacted via email and not phone as working nights so I will not be able to answer the phone. Voicemail can be left and I’ll call back when available.\nMany thanks.'),(4164,1087,'_form_id','1'),(4165,1087,'_seq_num','15'),(4166,1088,'_field_1','Hussain Ahmed'),(4167,1088,'_field_2','hussain@theteacherstraining.com'),(4168,1088,'_field_5','2045156229'),(4169,1088,'_field_3','Hi,\n\nLooking to enhance your e-learning offerings without overspending? At The Teachers Training, we offer CPD-accredited courses, white-label solutions, and custom designs tailored to your needs all at a reduced cost.\n\nLet’s explore how we can help grow your business. Are you available for a quick call?\n'),(4170,1088,'_form_id','1'),(4171,1088,'_seq_num','15'),(4172,1089,'_field_1','Hussain Ahmed'),(4173,1089,'_field_2','hussain@theteacherstraining.com'),(4174,1089,'_field_5','02045156229'),(4175,1089,'_field_3','\nHi,\n\nLooking to enhance your e-learning offerings without overspending? At The Teachers Training, we offer CPD-accredited courses, white-label solutions, and custom designs tailored to your needs all at a reduced cost.\n\nLet’s explore how we can help grow your business. Are you available for a quick call?'),(4176,1089,'_form_id','1'),(4177,1089,'_seq_num','15'),(4178,1090,'_field_1','Sarah Leggett'),(4179,1090,'_field_2','littlesarahleggett@gmail.com'),(4180,1090,'_field_5',''),(4181,1090,'_field_3','Hi,\n\nPlease can I get a price for an i7 10700k, 32gb ram, GeForce rtx 2080, 8gb vram, 1tb storage?\n\nBest wishes,\nSarah '),(4182,1090,'_form_id','1'),(4183,1090,'_seq_num','15'),(4184,1091,'_field_1','Matthew '),(4185,1091,'_field_2','mattycombs@hotmail.co.uk'),(4186,1091,'_field_5','07746219849'),(4187,1091,'_field_3','Hi.\nI was just wondering if you could have a look at my laptop. It\'s an asus tuf fx506h. I have had this laptop just over a year and it\'s worked fine. But I\'ve tried playing the new stalker 2 and it\'s just stuttering and unplayable. I\'ve downloaded all updates but nothing changed. I have just put a 16gb ram card in the free slot. Also the battery light and hdd light doesn\'t seem to work now either.\nAny help would be greatly appreciated.\n\nThank you.\n\nMatthew combs.'),(4188,1091,'_form_id','1'),(4189,1091,'_seq_num','15'),(4190,1092,'_field_1','Rafi Ahmad'),(4191,1092,'_field_2','rafi.ahmad@ebitlogix.com'),(4192,1092,'_field_5','+4402071837381'),(4193,1092,'_field_3','We\'re thrilled to introduce Bitlogix—a trusted partner in IT development and project management. \n\nImagine boosting your IT capabilities instantly, without the heavy costs. With 85+ skilled developers and 16 years of industry expertise, we’ve successfully delivered 250+ projects, helping businesses like yours save up to 70% on costs—all while maintaining top-tier quality.\n\nWhy wait? We offer a risk-free trial period, so you can see firsthand the value we bring. Let’s schedule a quick meeting to discuss how Bitlogix can accelerate your growth and streamline your IT needs. When is the best time for us to chat?'),(4194,1092,'_form_id','1'),(4195,1092,'_seq_num','15'),(4196,1093,'_field_1','Adrian Ravenscroft'),(4197,1093,'_field_2','adrian.ravens