ssi Katsavi'),(4251,1102,'_field_2','yossi.katsavi@brigex.com'),(4252,1102,'_field_5','6316010233'),(4253,1102,'_field_3','(Please forward to the person in charge of evaluating new partnerships at E-tec Computer Services)\n\nI am reaching out on behalf of FileHold(www.filehold.com) regarding possible reselling partnership.\n\nFileHold is a Canada based document management software developer with 450 customers worldwide.. \n\nWe are seeking partnerships with IT support providers, which will resell FileHold DMS to their clients and give 1st line support.\n\nFileHold is designed for medium to large organizations and offers an affordable alternative to other enterprise-grade DMS solutions.\n\nPlease let me know if you would be interested in learning more about this partnership offer.'),(4254,1102,'_form_id','1'),(4255,1102,'_seq_num','15'),(4256,1103,'_field_1','Deepak Amarnani'),(4257,1103,'_field_2','Webrank04@gmail.com'),(4258,1103,'_field_5','7077060205'),(4259,1103,'_field_3','Hi E-tecpc\n\nGreetings!\n\nI came across your website and would like to talk about SEO strategies.\n\nDuring my review, I noticed that your site is not ranking well on Google for any of your targeted keywords.\n\nAs you might already realize, this means your website is largely unnoticed by potential clients looking for suppliers in your industry.\n\nI can assist in elevating your site to the first page of Google, which will significantly boost your leads and sales.\n\nOur team has the capability to drive hundreds, or even thousands, of visitors to your website.\n\nIf you\'re interested, I can provide you with our pricing details, company information, and a competitive quote tailored to your needs.\n\nBest regards,  \nDeepak Amarnani'),(4260,1103,'_form_id','1'),(4261,1103,'_seq_num','15'),(4262,1104,'_field_1','Ricky Carder'),(4263,1104,'_field_2','Ricky.carder@Procompanypage.com'),(4264,1104,'_field_5','18149805065'),(4265,1104,'_field_3','\nWikipedia is considered to be the World’s most significant tool for reference material. The Wiki links show up on the 1st page of Google 97% of the time. With a Page on one of the most revered reference tools, you are sure to get yourself or your business noticed. So if you\'re thinking of getting a Wikipedia Page created, it\'s the best time of the year.\n\nIf you are interested in getting more information just respond back to this email.\n\nThanks,\n\nRicky Carder\nProfessional Company Page\nRicky.carder@Procompanypage.com\n\nRespond with stop to optout.'),(4266,1104,'_form_id','1'),(4267,1104,'_seq_num','15'),(4268,1105,'_field_1','Adrian Shaw'),(4269,1105,'_field_2','adrianandrachel2@hotmail.co.uk'),(4270,1105,'_field_5','+447864325360'),(4271,1105,'_field_3','My wife has lost a load of photos from her phone. Many of these are of her mum, in  the last few months of her life. She is desperate to get them back. We took the phone to Binary consultants in Glossop, where he retrieved lots of files and put them onto USB stick. Unfortunately neither us or him had the software to open the files. Is there any way you could help? My wife is desperate to get the pictures back if at all possible.\nMany thanks'),(4272,1105,'_form_id','1'),(4273,1105,'_seq_num','15'),(4274,1106,'_field_1','Michael O\'Malley'),(4275,1106,'_field_2','michael.malley@purchasing-aig.com'),(4276,1106,'_field_5','+447366345588'),(4277,1106,'_field_3','\n\n\n\n\nDear Sales/Account Team,\n\n          This correspondence serves as a formal request from American International Group. for a comprehensive quote and the establishment of a Net 30 payment account. As the SVP &amp; Global Chief Procurement Officer for American International Group. I am seeking your immediate attention to this matter.\n\nWe require confirmation of your current stock and vendor availability for the following IT items:\n\nZXP7 Ribbon YMCKO True Colour, High Yield 750 Image 800077-742\nIntel 14th GEN Core i9 Unlocked BX8071514900k\nCatalyst 9200L 24-port PoE+, 4 x 1G\n\nUpon receipt of your detailed quotation, our Purchase Order will be promptly issued, predicated on the agreed-upon Net 30 terms. Our standard payment policy for established vendor accounts is Net 30.\n\nWe anticipate your swift response and look forward to a productive partnership.\n\nSincerely,\n\nMichael O\'Malley\nSVP &amp; Global Chief Procurement Officer - Global Sourcing &amp; Global\nProcurement,American International Group (UK) Limited.\nThe AIG Building,\n58 Fenchurch Street.\nLondon EC3M 4AB England\nTel:+447366345588\n\n\n\n'),(4278,1106,'_form_id','1'),(4279,1106,'_seq_num','15'),(4280,1107,'_field_1','Sheila Vaughan'),(4281,1107,'_field_2','vaughansav@gmail.com'),(4282,1107,'_field_5','+447452938606'),(4283,1107,'_field_3','Hi, my Lenovo laptop screen has suddenly developed a black \"smudge\" bottom right and also a wide band of vertical lines - plus a smaller band of horizontal lines at the bottom. As I have only had it for 3 months (bought new) I went back to Argos to see if they could repair or replace the screen.  The lady there told me that such issues are usually caused by \"accidental damage\" and that the warranty would not cover it.   She recommended that I approach a computer repair service to see what they could suggest - and obviously pay for that.\nI see you are on Park Road Dukinfield which is quite close to where I live.  Is it possible for me to bring the computer in for you to take a look?\nWith kind regards,\nSheila Vaughan'),(4284,1107,'_form_id','1'),(4285,1107,'_seq_num','15'),(4286,1108,'_field_1','Deepak Amarnani'),(4287,1108,'_field_2','Siterank2@gmail.com'),(4288,1108,'_field_5','7077060205'),(4289,1108,'_field_3','Hey E-tecpc,\n\nWhen was the last time you searched for your own business on Google?\n\nI did it yesterday (for research), and I\'m guessing you\'re not thrilled with where you\'re showing up. Maybe page 2? Maybe buried on page 1 below competitors?\n\nI\'m Deepak, Marketing Head at a digital agency. We\'ve spent 10 years getting businesses to rank higher, and honestly, your situation doesn\'t look that complicated to fix.\n\nWhat I\'d like to do:\n•	Walk you through what\'s holding you back\n•	Share our portfolio of actual results we\'ve gotten\n•	Give you real pricing (no \"it depends\" answers)\n\nCall or email - you decide. Just send me:\n•	Email address\n•	Phone number (if talking\'s easier)\n•	Website\n\nSorry for the unsolicited message. I know your inbox is probably full of this stuff. But I actually looked at your site before reaching out, which is more than most people do.\n\nBest,\nDeepak\nMarketing Head\n\n'),(4290,1108,'_form_id','1'),(4291,1108,'_seq_num','15');
