15 16:08:52','',21,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/21-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(145,1,'2016-12-15 16:13:15','2016-12-15 16:13:15','e-tec Computer Services is a local business in Tameside, Greater Manchester, offering IT support. With over 20 years experience within the IT industry we use our IT knowledge to deliver a product that is competitively priced and built to excellent standards. We pride ourselves on our reputation and have an excellent client base built upon word-of-mouth recommendations within the Greater Manchester area\r\n\r\ne-tec Computer Services specialise in computer and laptop repairs, upgrades, data backups, network, support, tune-ups, new and refurbished PCs and laptops. We stock spare parts for all leading brands and are able to complete most repair jobs on the same day.\r\n\r\nWe cover all major brands including; Acer, Advent, Asus, Compaq, Dell, Emachines, E-system, Fujitsu, Hp, IBM, Lenovo, Medion, MSI, Packard Bell, Samsung, Sony and Toshiba.','e-TEC PC Computer Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2016-12-15 16:13:15','2016-12-15 16:13:15','',5,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(146,1,'2016-12-15 16:18:52','2016-12-15 16:18:52','Whether you have a software or hardware problem e-Tec Computer Services can repair any make of computer or laptop. With over 20 years of experience in the industry we are able to quickly diagnose and repair your equipment. We can provide an on-site service and will come to your office or home to get your computer or laptop quickly repaired.\n\nWe stock spare parts for all leading brands and are able to complete most repair jobs on the same day. Our repair computer and laptop repair service is competitively priced and we guarantee and fast turnaround without sacrificing on the quality of service.\n<h2>Software Repair</h2>\nUsing the latest diagnostic tools we can troubleshoot any software related problems you may be experiencing and recommend the appropriate solution. The software problems that we can repair are the following:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Failure to boot</li>\n 	<li>Blue screen issues</li>\n 	<li>Registry faults</li>\n 	<li>Corrupted operating system</li>\n 	<li>Corrupted drivers</li>\n 	<li>Removal of viruses, worms, trojans and spyware</li>\n 	<li>Data recovery and transfer of files from damaged hard drives to new drives</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Hardware Repair</h2>\nIf you are experiencing hardware issues with your computer or laptop we can quickly diagnose the fault and recommend the most cost effective repair. The hardware problems that we can repair are the following:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Motherboard replacement and repair</li>\n 	<li>HDD/SDD replacement and repair</li>\n 	<li>Memory replacement</li>\n 	<li>DVD/CD drive replacement</li>\n 	<li>Graphics card issues</li>\n 	<li>Laptop screen replacement</li>\n 	<li>Laptop hinge repairs</li>\n 	<li>Power socket replacement</li>\n 	<li>Replacement power adapter</li>\n 	<li>None boot issues</li>\n 	<li>Noisy fan</li>\n</ul>\nIf you are not sure what the problem is related to our team has the expertise to diagnose and troubleshoot the problem.\n\nWe are happy to provide a free quote with no hidden costs for any software or hardware issues that you are experiencing. <a href=\"/contact\">Contact us for more information</a> about our computer and laptop repair.','COMPUTER & LAPTOP REPAIRS','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-autosave-v1','','','2016-12-15 16:18:52','2016-12-15 16:18:52','',11,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/11-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(147,1,'2016-12-15 16:19:21','2016-12-15 16:19:21','Whether you have a software or hardware problem e-Tec Computer Services can repair any make of computer or laptop. With over 20 years of experience in the industry we are able to quickly diagnose and repair your equipment. We can provide an on-site service and will come to your office or home to get your computer or laptop quickly repaired.\r\n\r\nWe stock spare parts for all leading brands and are able to complete most repair jobs on the same day. Our repair computer and laptop repair service is competitively priced and we guarantee and fast turnaround without sacrificing on the quality of service.\r\n<h2>Software Repair</h2>\r\nUsing the latest diagnostic tools we can troubleshoot any software related problems you may be experiencing and recommend the appropriate solution. The software problems that we can repair are the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Failure to boot</li>\r\n 	<li>Blue screen issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Registry faults</li>\r\n 	<li>Corrupted operating system</li>\r\n 	<li>Corrupted drivers</li>\r\n 	<li>Removal of viruses, worms, trojans and spyware</li>\r\n 	<li>Data recovery and transfer of files from damaged hard drives to new drives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Hardware Repair</h2>\r\nIf you are experiencing hardware issues with your computer or laptop we can quickly diagnose the fault and recommend the most cost effective repair. The hardware problems that we can repair are the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Motherboard replacement and repair</li>\r\n 	<li>HDD/SDD replacement and repair</li>\r\n 	<li>Memory replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>DVD/CD drive replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Graphics card issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop screen replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop hinge repairs</li>\r\n 	<li>Power socket replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Replacement power adapter</li>\r\n 	<li>None boot issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Noisy fan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you are not sure what the problem is related to our team has the expertise to diagnose and troubleshoot the problem.\r\n\r\nWe are happy to provide a free quote with no hidden costs for any software or hardware issues that you are experiencing. <a href=\"/contact\">Contact us for more information</a> about our computer and laptop repair.','COMPUTER & LAPTOP REPAIRS','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2016-12-15 16:19:21','2016-12-15 16:19:21','',11,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0