client base built upon word-of-mouth recommendations within the Greater Manchester area\r\n\r\ne-tec Computer Services specialise in computer and laptop repairs, upgrades, data backups, network, support, tune-ups, new and refurbished PCs and laptops. We stock spare parts for all leading brands and are able to complete most repair jobs on the same day.\r\n\r\nWe cover all major brands including; Acer, Advent, Asus, Compaq, Dell, Emachines, E-system, Fujitsu, Hp, IBM, Lenovo, Medion, MSI, Packard Bell, Samsung, Sony and Toshiba.','e-TEC Computer Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2017-01-06 14:21:44','2017-01-06 14:21:44','',5,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(221,1,'2017-01-06 14:22:24','2017-01-06 14:22:24','e-tec Computer Services is a local business in Tameside, Greater Manchester, offering IT support. With over 20 years experience within the IT industry we use our IT knowledge to deliver a product that is competitively priced and built to excellent standards. We pride ourselves on our reputation and have an excellent client base built upon word-of-mouth recommendations within the Greater Manchester area\r\n\r\ne-tec Computer Services specialise in computer and laptop repairs, upgrades, data backups, network, support, tune-ups, new and refurbished PCs and laptops. We stock spare parts for all leading brands and are able to complete most repair jobs on the same day.\r\n\r\nWe cover all major brands including; Acer, Advent, Asus, Compaq, Dell, Emachines, E-system, Fujitsu, Hp, IBM, Lenovo, Medion, MSI, Packard Bell, Samsung, Sony and Toshiba.','e-TEC Computer Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2017-01-06 14:22:24','2017-01-06 14:22:24','',5,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(240,2,'2011-01-14 13:42:14','2011-01-14 13:42:14','If computer repair Denton or laptop repair Denton is what you are looking for, why not consider <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">E-tec Computer Services.</a>\r\n\r\nIn addition to computer repair and laptop repair we also offer the following services:\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Custom built computers</li>\r\n 	<li>Virus removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Pc security</li>\r\n 	<li>Servicing</li>\r\n 	<li>Internet setup</li>\r\n 	<li>Networking</li>\r\n 	<li>Data recovery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe undertake more than computer repair and laptop repair; we optimize your computer or laptop to run faster and more reliably whilst eliminating any problems you may have. We can inspect your computer or laptop and recommend any upgrades, software or hardware that would improve their performance.\r\n\r\nAs we are a local computer repair Denton company, we can therefore respond to any computer problems extremely quickly.\r\n\r\nShould you require further information, please feel free to call us on 0161 339 6523 or email <a title=\"info@e-tecp.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:info@e-tecp.co.uk\">info@e-tecp.co.uk</a>','Computer Repair Denton','','publish','closed','open','','computer-repair-denton','','','2021-12-03 14:33:35','2021-12-03 14:33:35','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=240',0,'post','',0),(244,1,'2017-01-09 14:19:19','2017-01-09 14:19:19','','abc-blue','','inherit','closed','closed','','abc-blue','','','2017-01-09 14:19:19','2017-01-09 14:19:19','',0,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/abc-blue.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(245,1,'2017-01-09 14:19:19','2017-01-09 14:19:19','','cyber-pulse-logo','','inherit','closed','closed','','cyber-pulse-logo','','','2017-01-09 14:19:19','2017-01-09 14:19:19','',0,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cyber-pulse-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(246,1,'2017-01-09 14:19:20','2017-01-09 14:19:20','','climatech-logo','','inherit','closed','closed','','climatech-logo','','','2017-01-09 14:19:20','2017-01-09 14:19:20','',0,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2017