4','2012-04-30 20:12:54','e-tec computer services safeguards precious video assets for Standby Productions\r\n\r\n<strong>Company: </strong>Standby Productions\r\n\r\n<strong>Location: </strong>24 School Lane, Didsbury, M20 6RG\r\n\r\n<strong>Industry: </strong><a title=\"Video Production Manchester\" href=\"http://www.standbyproductions.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Video Production Manchester</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Official Website: </strong>http://www.standbyproductions.co.uk/\r\n\r\n<strong>Challenges:</strong>\r\n\r\n\"As a Video Production company we deal with large files all day every day that eat hard drives like there\'s no tomorrow, so we set e-tec computer services quite a challenge by asking them to fit a system that not only stored such large files but also streamed them and backed them up quickly and effectively. We also needed the files to be available to more than one machine, again at high speed, so that there was no \'stuttering\' when playing any High Definition footage.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<strong>Solutions:</strong>\r\n\r\n\"E-tec Computer Services provided a NAS Server with 12 terabyte of storage, networked all our Macs together so that now any Editor that enters the studio can log in and access all the rushes and associated project files instantly and begin cutting. e-tec computer services did this quickly and efficiently. I am really impressed with the way it has all come together, providing what looks like the perfect system.\"\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Simon Owen - Standby Productions</strong></p>','A Word From Standby Productions','','publish','closed','open','','a-word-from-standby-productions-2','','','2021-12-03 14:26:58','2021-12-03 14:26:58','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=615',0,'post','',0),(634,2,'2012-05-15 10:41:18','2012-05-15 09:41:18','Recently a number of customers have told <a title=\"computer repair Stalybridge\" href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/computer-repair-stalybridge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">E-tec Computer Services</a> they have received a phone call from Microsoft stating that they have a problem with their computer and they can help. Don’t get caught out.\r\n\r\nCriminals often use the names of well-known companies, like Microsoft, BT, TalkTalk etc in their scams. They use the company names to convince you to give them money or your personal information. While traditionally they have used email to trick you, they are now using the telephone more and more to try and get your details.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nCommon scams that use company names\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Someone from \"Microsoft/BT/TalkTalk Tech Support\" calls to fix your computer</li>\r\n 	<li>You receive a call to telling you that you have won the Lottery\"</li>\r\n 	<li>The company requires credit card information to validate your copy of Windows or other software installed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Avoid these dangerous hoaxes</strong>\r\n\r\nThe companies above do not send unsolicited email messages or make unsolicited phone calls to request personal or financial information or to fix your computer.\r\n\r\nIf you receive an unsolicited email message or phone call that says it’s from one of the companies above or any other large company for that matter and requests that you send personal information or click links to websites, delete the message or hang up the phone.\r\n\r\nLarge companies do not make unsolicited phone calls to help you fix your computer\r\n\r\nIn this scam criminals call you and claim to be from Technical Support. They offer to help solve your computer problems. Once the crooks have gained your trust, they attempt to steal from you and damage your computer with malicious software including viruses and spyware.\r\n\r\nAlthough the police can trace phone numbers, criminals often use pay phones, disposable mobile phones, or stolen mobile phone numbers. It\'s better to avoid being conned rather than try to repair the damage afterwards.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Treat all unsolicited phone calls with scepticism.</li>\r\n 	<li> Do not provide any personal information.</li>\r\n 	<li>If you receive an unsolicited call from someone claiming to be from Technical Support, hang up.</li>\r\n 	<li>If you think you might be a victim of fraud, report it to the police.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPlease don’t get caught out, I have had a number of calls on this issue and a number of my customers have already reported to me that they have been contacted. It’s better to be safe than sorry so put the phone down on them, call the company back who they say they are from and ask them if they would have contacted you in this way.','Avoid Fraudulent Telephone Scams','','publish','closed','open','','avoid-fraudulent-telephone-scams','','','2021-12-03 14:25:54','2021-12-03 14:25:54','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=634',0,'post','',0),(664,2,'2012-09-20 19:47:55','2012-09-20 18:47:55','Problems sending and receiving email on Outlook when using @btconnect.com e-mail address.\r\n\r\nIf you are having problems sending and/or receiving emails using @btconnect.com e-mail address using a mail program such as Outlook, the most likely reason is to BT\'s migration from their current e-mail servers over to Office 365.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nBT Business is moving customers onto a new and improved email service powered by Microsoft Office 365. Unfortunately there is no option not to be migrated over to the new servers, as BT are updating and replacing there old servers to this new e-mail platform.\r\n\r\nOnce the migration has been made your email client such as Outlook will stop working until it has been updated with the new server settings. If you require help with Outlook to work again get in touch and e-tec computer services will be able to reconfigure your server settings so you will be able to send and receive emails once again.','Outlook not working with @btconnect.com e-mail address','','publish','closed','open','','outlook-not-working-with-btconnect-com-e-mail-address','','','2017-01-16 17:08:23','2017-01-16 17:08:23','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=664',0,'post','',0),(675,2,'2013-03-16 00:31:37','2013-03-16 00:31:37','We can upgrade your PC or Laptop to Windows 7 or 8 so that you\'re getting the latest and greatest features to work with.\r\n\r\n<strong><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-912\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Win-7-8-300x172.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"172\" />A few great benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>New operating system installed</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>User accounts set up</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Security settings configured</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New features</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your PC or Laptop is a few years old the chances are that you’ll be running an older version of the operating system. This means that you could be missing out on some of the latest support for new technology and software.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nUpgrading to Microsoft Windows 7 or 8 will mean that you’re making the most of your computer and all the features and benefits that the latest technology has to offer.\r\n\r\nOur Operating System Upgrade service is designed for Windows Desktops &amp; Laptops.\r\n\r\n<strong>The service includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">E-tec Computer Services</a> will check to see if your PC or Laptop will work with the upgrade</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Let you know if your computer needs any hardware upgrades to allow it work with the operating system upgrade</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Backup your files to make sure they’re safe</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll upgrade any hardware if you asked us to do so</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll install Windows 7 or 8</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Set up any user accounts you asked us to set up for you</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Install any updates to make sure you’ve got the latest features and security patches</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Restore your files from the backup</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Test that your computer is working as expected</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll show some of the new features and answer any questions you may have</strong></li>\r\n</ul>','Operating System Upgrade and Check','','publish','closed','open','','operating-system-upgrade-check','','','2021-12-03 14:25:02','2021-12-03 14:25:02','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=675',0,'post','',0),(751,2,'2013-03-17 21:07:51','2013-03-17 21:07:51','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-907\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/shield-security-icon-300x286.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"286\" />If your computer is infected with a virus, spyware, malware or other Internet nasties don\'t worry. Our virus and spyware removal service will track down and remove those bugs.\r\n\r\n<strong>A few great benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ideal For Infected PCs / Laptops</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Remove Viruses, Spyware, Malware, Trojans </strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Install Anti-virus / Internet Security </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nViruses, Spyware, Malware and Trojans – all words that no computer users wants to hear. These nasty little bugs can cause all sorts of problems for people, from minor annoyance, to file loss and identity theft.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> are experts at removing Viruses, Spyware and Malware If your computer is infected then our Virus and Spyware Removal service is just for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>The service includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Scan your computer using our special software to locate any viruses, spyware and malware</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Remove anything harmful we find on your computer</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Install Anti-virus / Internet Security</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Leave you with a report explaining what we did during the service</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;','Virus Protection and Data Security','','publish','closed','open','','virus-protection-and-data-security','','','2021-12-03 14:23:36','2021-12-03 14:23:36','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=751',0,'post','',0),(801,2,'2014-03-31 13:33:33','2014-03-31 12:33:33','<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-905\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lenovo_thinkcentre_edge72-rua-300x197.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" />Looking for a new Desktop PC or Laptop for home or business? Then we can help.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re looking for a Desktop or Laptop, for personal or business use, e-tec computer services are able to provide a solution for your needs. We have an excellent choice of new and refurbished units.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe have a great range of Desktops and Laptops PCs from leading brands such as Samsung and Lenovo.\r\n\r\nIf gaming is top priority then you should consider one of our Custom Built Gaming PCs. These powerful computers come with faster processors, large memory and hard drive capacity as well as superior graphics cards for blazing response times.\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for cheap computers, with top specifications, then choose one of our refurbished PCs. These bargain desktop computers have been professionally checked with the operating system restored to factory state.\r\n\r\nIt can be difficult and confusing when choosing the right computing device. With a multitude of Desktop PCs and Laptops on offer we’ll be able help you choose the right one that best suits your needs.\r\n\r\ne-tec computer services are based in River Mill Business Centre\r\nPark Road, Dukinfield, SK16 5LR and are available on 0845 475 1335 or 07977 697 099.','New Desktop PCs & Laptops','','publish','closed','open','','new-pcs-laptops','','','2021-12-03 14:22:22','2021-12-03 14:22:22','',0,'http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/?p=801',0,'post','',0),(834,2,'2014-02-15 17:14:01','2014-02-15 17:14:01','Windows XP SP3 and Office 2003 will no