\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> to assess your PC and offer the best options to meet your needs, please <a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/contact/\">contact us</a>.\n\nSupport for Windows XP ends in…. <a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/enterprise/endofsupport.aspx\">http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/enterprise/endofsupport.aspx</a>','Support for Windows XP will end on April 8, 2014','','inherit','closed','closed','','834-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 16:16:42','2017-01-16 16:16:42','',834,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/834-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(839,1,'2017-01-16 16:17:05','2017-01-16 16:17:05','<span style=\"color: #3366ff\"><strong>Acer Dell Hp Compaq Packard Bell Lenovo Samsung Toshiba Sony and many more......</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are looking for a fast, efficient and competitively priced <strong>laptop repair service</strong>, e-tec computer services is your best choice. Whether you have software or hardware problems, want to upgrade your laptop or need to recover lost data, e-tec computer services is here to help you. We have been providing private homes and businesses throughout Greater Manchester with a quality service for over ten years.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>We can help with:</strong></span>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Laptop Screen Replacement</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>None Boot Issues</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Memory Faults</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Power Socket Replacement</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Replacement Adapter</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Motherboard Repair</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Hard Drive Repair - Replacement</strong></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000\"><stron