rease to over 70°C. If you aren\'t familiar with these numbers, then I will tell you that this is simply awful. It\'s probably the reason why one could heat their entire bedroom in the winter just by turning on this system. Compare this to a custom built pc with 3 case fans, not including the heatsink and fan for the Quad Core processor that it includes. This CPU runs idles at about 35°C. Much improved. In fact, over 20°C improved. So much for the \"quality\" components that are sold at retail.','Custom Built Computer','','inherit','closed','closed','','257-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 16:26:44','2017-01-16 16:26:44','',257,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/257-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(859,1,'2017-01-16 16:27:02','2017-01-16 16:27:02','If <strong>computer repair Denton</strong> or <strong>laptop repair Denton</strong> is what you are looking for, why not consider <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">e-tec computer services.</a>\n\nIn addition to <strong>computer repair</strong> and <strong>laptop repair</strong> we also offer the following services:\n<ul>\n	<li>Computer upgrades</li>\n	<li>Laptop upgrades</li>\n	<li>Custom built computers</li>\n	<li>Virus removal</li>\n	<li>Pc security</li>\n	<li>Servicing</li>\n	<li>Internet setup</li>\n	<li>Networking</li>\n	<li>Data recovery</li>\n</ul>\nWe undertake more than <strong>computer repair</strong> and <strong>laptop repair</strong>; we optimize your computer or laptop to run faster and more reliably whilst eliminating any problems you may have. We can inspect your computer or laptop and recommend any upgrades, software or hardware that would improve their performance.\n\nAs we are a local <strong>computer repair Denton </strong>company, we can therefore respond to any computer problems extremely quickly.\n\nShould you require further information, please feel free to call us on 0161 339 6523 or email <a title=\"info@e-tecp.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:info@e-tecp.co.uk\">info@e-tecp.co.uk</a>','Computer Repai