that you\'re getting the latest and greatest features to work with.\r\n\r\n<strong><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-912\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Win-7-8-300x172.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"172\" />A few great benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>New operating system installed</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>User accounts set up</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Security settings configured</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New features</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your PC or Laptop is a few years old the chances are that you’ll be running an older version of the operating system. This means that you could be missing out on some of the latest support for new technology and software.\r\n\r\nUpgrading to Microsoft Windows 7 or 8 will mean that you’re making the most of your computer and all the features and benefits that the latest technology has to offer.\r\n\r\nOur Operating System Upgrade service is designed for Windows Desktops &amp; Laptops.\r\n\r\n<strong>The service includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> will check to see if your PC or Laptop will work with the upgrade</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Let you know if your computer needs any hardware upgrades to allow it work with the operating system upgrade</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Backup your files to make sure they’re safe</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll upgrade any hardware if you asked us to do so</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll install Windows 7 or 8</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Set up any user accounts you asked us to set up for you</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Install any updates to make sure you’ve got the latest features and security patches</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Restore your files from the backup</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Test that your computer is working as expected</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>We’ll show some of the new features and answer any questions you may have</strong></li>\r\n</ul>','Operating System Upgrade and Check','','inherit','closed','closed','','675-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:03:48','2017-01-16 17:03:48','',675,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/675-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(914,1,'2017-01-16 17:04:05','2017-01-16 17:04:05','','Custom-PC','','inherit','closed','closed','','custom-pc','','','2017-01-16 17:04:16','2017-01-16 17:04:16','',327,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Custom-PC.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(915,1,'2017-01-16 17:04:09','2017-01-16 17:04:09','Bespoke Computers\n\nAre you looking for a custom built computer, desktop computer, an extreme gaming computer or Media Centre pc? Then you need look no further.\n\n<a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk\" target=\"_self\">e-tec computer services</a> specialises in custom built pcs, gaming pcs, desktop computers and media centre pcs.\n\nUsing the very best quality components, we pride ourselves in offering excellent value for money.\n\nWhether your requirements are for small business/home office, running Word/Excel/Accounting package applications, etc, or for personal use such as homework/school work/internet browsing, we are able to provide the perfect solution.\n\nAll systems are individually assembled and designed to be quiet, reliable, energy efficient and top performing.<a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/Intel-Sandybridge.gif\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-329 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/Intel-Sandybridge-150x150.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>','Custom Built Computer/PC systems','','inherit','closed','closed','','327-autosave-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:04:09','2017-01-16 17:04:09','',327,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/327-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(916,1,'2017-01-16 17:04:31','2017-01-16 17:04:31','','Intel-Sandybridge-150x150','','inherit','closed','closed','','intel-sandybridge-150x150','','','2017-01-16 17:04:31','2017-01-16 17:04:31','',0,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Intel-Sandybridge-150x150.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(917,1,'2017-01-16 17:04:44','2017-01-16 17:04:44','','Intel-Sandybridge-150x150','','inherit','closed','closed','','intel-sandybridge-150x150-2','','','2017-01-16 17:04:44','2017-01-16 17:04:44','',327,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Intel-Sandybridge-150x150.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(918,1,'2017-01-16 17:04:55','2017-01-16 17:04:55','Bespoke Computers\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-914\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Custom-PC-212x300.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"300\" />Are you looking for a custom built computer, desktop computer, an extreme gaming computer or Media Centre pc? Then you need look no further.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk\" target=\"_self\">e-tec computer services</a> specialises in custom built pcs, gaming pcs, desktop computers and media centre pcs.\r\n\r\nUsing the very best quality components, we pride ourselves in offering excellent value for money.\r\n\r\nWhether your requirements are for small business/home office, running Word/Excel/Accounting package applications, etc, or for personal use such as homework/school work/internet browsing, we are able to provide the perfect solution.\r\n\r\nAll systems are individually assembled and designed to be quiet, reliable, energy efficient and top performing.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-917\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Intel-Sandybridge-150x150.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />','Custom Built Computer/PC systems','','inherit','closed','closed','','327-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:04:55','2017-01-16 17:04:55','',327,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/327-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(919,1,'2017-01-16 17:05:11','2017-01-16 17:05:11','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Reliable <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">custom built pcs</a>, quality hardware, awesome prices...</p>\n<strong>e-tec computer services</strong> use their knowledge of computing to bring the customer a high quality product, at a lower price than leading competitors.\n\nWe design and build your system to your exact specification, giving you full control over what goes into your system, thus making it your perfect pc.\n\nbenefits of a <strong>custom built pc  </strong>\n\nComputer manufacturers such as Acer, Dell, HP, etc, have come a long way in providing consumers with a number of options for building custom computer systems. Whilst these computers may be adequate for the typical user, you might want a system that can be used for years, after purchase. This being the case, you should definitely consider a custom built computer.\n\nMost manufacturers use proprietary hardware within their pcs, which can make it extremely difficult to perform upgrades to your system; the various components become obsolete or are not compatible, for example CPUs, RAM, sound and video adapters. Whilst some of these components are upgradable, after the initial purchase, it is often the case that your upgrade options are very limited.\n\nA <strong>custom built computer</strong> allows you the most flexibility. Taking into consideration the quality of the components used in a custom built system, the cost is often less than buying a pre-built system of the same specifications.\n\nAnother advantage of a custom built pc is that you are able to start with a very basic system using a low end CPU, perhaps combined with a mid-range system board and minimal memory. You could also start with a system board that has on-board sound and video. Eventually, you may decide to add or upgrade to better components.\n\nA custom built computer would probably last you a few years before it ‘feels outdated’. At this time, instead of buying a whole new computer you would only need to, at most, swap a few components to make it ‘feel up-to-date’ again.\n\nWhy Buy From Us?\n\nWe consider our services to be amongst the most inexpensive in the UK. Not only do we offer incredible prices, but all of our top quality hardware is sourced from reliable and well known suppliers.\n\nWe DO NOT use cheap components in order to cut down on costs.\n\nOur systems are built using the best quality hardware together with reliable and high performance components.','Benefits of a Custom Built PC','','inherit','closed','closed','','255-autosave-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:05:11','2017-01-16 17:05:11','',255,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/255-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(920,1,'2017-01-16 17:05:12','2017-01-16 17:05:12','','PC-Case-01-e1293547461909','','inherit','closed','closed','','pc-case-01-e1293547461909','','','2017-01-16 17:05:12','2017-01-16 17:05:12','',255,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/PC-Case-01-e1293547461909.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(921,1,'2017-01-16 17:05:33','2017-01-16 17:05:33','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-920 size-medium\" src=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/PC-Case-01-e1293547461909-150x300.gif\" width=\"150\" height=\"300\" />Reliable <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">custom built pcs</a>, quality hardware, awesome prices...</p>\r\n<strong>e-tec computer services</strong> use their knowledge of computing to bring the customer a high quality product, at a lower price than leading competitors.\r\n\r\nWe design and build your system to your exact specification, giving you full control over what goes into your system, thus making it your perfect pc.\r\n\r\nbenefits of a <strong>custom built pc  </strong>\r\n\r\nComputer manufacturers such as Acer, Dell, HP, etc, have come a long way in providing consumers with a number of options for building custom computer systems. Whilst these computers may be adequate for the typical user, you might want a system that can be used for years, after purchase. This being the case, you should definitely consider a custom built computer.\r\n\r\nMost manufacturers use proprietary hardware within their pcs, which can make it extremely difficult to perform upgrades to your system; the various components become obsolete or are not compatible, for example CPUs, RAM, sound and video adapters. Whilst some of these components are upgradable, after the initial purchase, it is often the case that your upgrade options are very limited.\r\n\r\nA <strong>custom built computer</strong> allows you the most flexibility. Taking into consideration the quality of the components used in a custom built system, the cost is often less than buying a pre-built system of the same specifications.\r\n\r\nAnother advantage of a custom built pc is that you are able to start with a very basic system using a low end CPU, perhaps combined with a mid-range system board and minimal memory. You could also start with a system board that has on-board sound and video. Eventually, you may decide to add or upgrade to better components.\r\n\r\nA custom built computer would probably last you a few years before it ‘feels outdated’. At this time, instead of buying a whole new computer you would only need to, at most, swap a few components to make it ‘feel up-to-date’ again.\r\n\r\nWhy Buy From Us?\r\n\r\nWe consider our services to be amongst the most inexpensive in the UK. Not only do we offer incredible prices, but all of our top quality hardware is sourced from reliable and well known suppliers.\r\n\r\nWe DO NOT use cheap components in order to cut down on costs.\r\n\r\nOur systems are built using the best quality hardware together with reliable and high performance components.','Benefits of a Custom Built PC','','inherit','closed','closed','','255-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:05:33','2017-01-16 17:05:33','',255,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/255-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(922,1,'2017-01-16 17:05:50','2017-01-16 17:05:50','','Image','','inherit','closed','closed','','image','','','2017-01-16 17:05:50','2017-01-16 17:05:50','',254,'http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Image.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(923,1,'2017-01-16 17:05:59','2017-01-16 17:05:59','<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-922\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Image-300x231.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"231\" />Solid-state hard drive (SSD)</strong>\r\n\r\nInstalling RAM (random access memory) has always been known as an easy way to boost your system’s performance.\r\n\r\nSSDs (solid state drives) on the other hand, are now much more affordable and a <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">laptop upgrade</a> and <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">computer upgrade</a> of your hard drive to an SSD drive has become an even easier way to maximise your computer’s performance.\r\n\r\n<strong>benefits of solid state drives</strong>\r\nYou may be wondering why SSDs are all the ‘rage’. What makes them superior?\r\n\r\nThe benefits of a <strong>laptop upgrade</strong> or <strong>computer upgrade</strong> to an SSD are numerous, the major one being the increased performance for ‘read access’, and it is this that interests most people.  Other benefits are listed below:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Unlike traditional hard drives, SSDs have no movable parts and are, therefore, better in handling ‘drops’ and ‘knocks’.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs tend to be more power efficient, and often they can increase the battery life of laptops and netbooks.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs are usually more lightweight than traditional hard drives which in turn mean lighter products.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs operate more quietly than traditional hard drives and, because they have no moving parts, generate less heat and tend to have longer life spans.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>performance</strong>\r\nThe areas, in terms of performance, where SSDs really shine are most noticeable when launching applications, booting up and shutting down your computer. A laptop upgrade and computer upgrade to an SSD makes your computer/laptop feel twice as fast when performing these operations.\r\n\r\nA laptop upgrade and computer upgrade to an SSD makes computing an invariably more enjoyable experience, especially if you, like most people, find yourself impatiently tapping your fingers every time the computer starts up or an application loads.\r\n\r\n<strong>Intel’s X-25M Solid-State Drive</strong>\r\n\r\nIntel has spent years perfecting and optimising their SSDs and are definitely one of the leaders in the SSD industry.\r\n\r\nThe Intel X-25M is, in particular, a top-of-the-line SSD in the mobility space.\r\n\r\nAlthough not a first generation device, on paper the Intel X-25M advertises ‘read speeds’ of up to 250 MB/s and ‘write speeds’ up to 70 MB/s.','Solid State Drive Upgrade','','inherit','closed','closed','','254-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:05:59','2017-01-16 17:05:59','',254,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/254-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(924,1,'2017-01-16 17:07:43','2017-01-16 17:07:43','<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-905\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lenovo_thinkcentre_edge72-rua-300x197.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"197\" />Looking for a new Desktop PC or Laptop for home or business? Then we can help.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re looking for a Desktop or Laptop, for personal or business use, e-tec computer services are able to provide a solution for your needs. We have an excellent choice of new and refurbished units.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe have a great range of Desktops and Laptops PCs from leading brands such as Samsung and Lenovo.\r\n\r\nIf gaming is top priority then you should consider one of our Custom Built Gaming PCs. These powerful computers come with faster processors, large memory and hard drive capacity as well as superior graphics cards for blazing response times.\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for cheap computers, with top specifications, then choose one of our refurbished PCs. These bargain desktop computers have been professionally checked with the operating system restored to factory state.\r\n\r\nIt can be difficult and confusing when choosing the right computing device. With a multitude of Desktop PCs and Laptops on offer we’ll be able help you choose the right one that best suits your needs.\r\n\r\ne-tec computer services are based in River Mill Business Centre\r\nPark Road, Dukinfield, SK16 5LR and are available on 0845 475 1335 or 07977 697 099.','New Desktop PCs & Laptops','','inherit','closed','closed','','801-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:07:43','2017-01-16 17:07:43','',801,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/801-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(925,1,'2017-01-16 17:07:48','2017-01-16 17:07:48','Windows XP SP3 and Office 2003 will no longer be supported by Microsoft after 8th April 2014.\r\n\r\nFrom 8th April, 2014, technical assistance for Windows XP SP3 and Office 2003 will no longer be available from Microsoft, including automatic updates that help protect your PC. If you continue to use Windows XP, your computer might become more vulnerable to security risks and viruses.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\ne-tec computer services are able to assist you in upgrading to a updated PC. If your current PC meets the system requirements we can help you upgrade your operating system to Windows 7 or Windows 8 and migrate all you data.\r\n\r\nIf your PC does not meet system requirements, we can assist you with purchasing a new PC with Windows 7 or Windows 8 and migrating all your current data.\r\n\r\nIf you would like <a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> to assess your PC and offer the best options to meet your needs, please <a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/contact/\">contact us</a>.\r\n\r\nSupport for Windows XP ends in…. <a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/enterprise/endofsupport.aspx\">http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/enterprise/endofsupport.aspx</a>','Support for Windows XP will end on April 8, 2014','','inherit','closed','closed','','834-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:07:48','2017-01-16 17:07:48','',834,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/834-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(926,1,'2017-01-16 17:07:55','2017-01-16 17:07:55','Acer, Dell, Hp, Compaq, Packard Bell, Lenovo, Samsung, Toshiba Sony, and many more...\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a fast, efficient and competitively priced laptop repair service, e-tec computer services is your best choice. Whether you have software or hardware problems, want to upgrade your laptop or need to recover lost data, e-tec computer services is here to help you. We have been providing private homes and businesses throughout Greater Manchester with a quality service for over ten years.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe can help with:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Laptop Screen Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>None Boot Issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Memory Faults</li>\r\n 	<li>Power Socket Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Replacement Adapter</li>\r\n 	<li>Motherboard Repair</li>\r\n 	<li>Hard Drive Repair - Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop Hinge Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li>Software Issues - Operating System Failure</li>\r\n 	<li>Virus Removal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt e-tec computer services we believe in offering a high standard of customer support. Our laptop repair service is competitively priced and we guarantee a fast turnaround time, but this does not mean that we allow price considerations to affect the quality of our laptop repair work.\r\n\r\nWe use the most up-to-date diagnostic equipment to identify the cause of any faults in your laptop as quickly and accurately as possible. Then carry out the necessary repairs promptly, with most repairs being completed on the same day we receive your laptop.\r\n\r\nWith over 10 years of experience in the industry, e-tec computer services are able to diagnose and repair practically anything that could go wrong with any make of laptop.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> is able to provide an on-site service. We will come to your office or home and, where possible, will diagnose and repair your laptop as quickly as possible to get you up and running again.\r\n\r\nEven if you are not sure what the problem is, our team has expertise in troubleshooting and remedying all software problems, including blue screen, virus removal, registry issues, corrupted hard drives and operating system failure. If your laptop is physically damaged and cannot be repaired or your hard drive crashes, we can carry out Data Recovery to retrieve your data files and transfer them to a new hard drive.\r\n<h4></h4>','Laptop Repair','','inherit','closed','closed','','411-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:07:55','2017-01-16 17:07:55','',411,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/411-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(927,1,'2017-01-16 17:08:01','2017-01-16 17:08:01','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-907\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/shield-security-icon-300x286.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"286\" />If your computer is infected with a virus, spyware, malware or other Internet nasties don\'t worry. Our virus and spyware removal service will track down and remove those bugs.\r\n\r\n<strong>A few great benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ideal For Infected PCs / Laptops</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Remove Viruses, Spyware, Malware, Trojans </strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Install Anti-virus / Internet Security </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nViruses, Spyware, Malware and Trojans – all words that no computer users wants to hear. These nasty little bugs can cause all sorts of problems for people, from minor annoyance, to file loss and identity theft.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">e-tec computer services</a> are experts at removing Viruses, Spyware and Malware If your computer is infected then our Virus and Spyware Removal service is just for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>The service includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Scan your computer using our special software to locate any viruses, spyware and malware</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Remove 