at you are looking for then why not consider e-tec computer services.','Computer Repair Chorlton-cum-Hardy','','inherit','closed','closed','','258-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:23','2017-01-16 17:10:23','',258,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/258-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(945,1,'2017-01-16 17:10:28','2017-01-16 17:10:28','The typical user of a retail pc would be less likely to trust a custom built computer than their system. However, this logic is faulty. While there is chance that something may go wrong with a <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk\" target=\"_self\">custom built system</a>, the chances are very slim. The cheap cooling systems and weak power supplies found in retail units is just one of the reasons why custom built pcs are becoming more popular with each passing month.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFor comparison, a well known brand retail pc runs with a 300watt power supply and one case fan in the back. The Quad Core processor in the system runs idle at 58°C. Put a load on this CPU for more than a few minutes and the temps increase to over 70°C. If you aren\'t familiar with these numbers, then I will tell you that this is simply awful. It\'s probably the reason why one could heat their entire bedroom in the winter just by turning on this system.\r\n\r\nCompare this to a custom built pc with 3 case fans, not including the heatsink and fan for the Quad Core processor that it includes. This CPU runs idles at about 35°C. Much improved. In fact, over 20°C improved. So much for the \"quality\" components that are sold at retail.','Custom Built Computer','','inherit','closed','closed','','257-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:28','2017-01-16 17:10:28','',257,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/257-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(946,1,'2017-01-16 17:10:35','2017-01-16 17:10:35','If computer repair Denton or laptop repair Denton is what you are looking for, why not consider <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">e-tec computer services.</a>\r\n\r\nIn addition to computer repair and laptop repair we also offer the following services:\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Custom built computers</li>\r\n 	<li>Virus removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Pc security</li>\r\n 	<li>Servicing</li>\r\n 	<li>Internet setup</li>\r\n 	<li>Networking</li>\r\n 	<li>Data recovery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe undertake more than computer repair and laptop repair; we optimize your computer or laptop to run faster and more reliably whilst eliminating any problems you may have. We can inspect your computer or laptop and recommend any upgrades, software or hardware that would improve their performance.\r\n\r\nAs we are a local computer repair Denton company, we can therefore respond to any computer problems extremely quickly.\r\n\r\nShould you require further information, please feel free to call us on 0161 339 6523 or email <a title=\"info@e-tecp.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:info@e-tecp.co.uk\">info@e-tecp.co.uk</a>','Computer Repair Denton','','inherit','closed','closed','','240-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:35','2017-01-16 17:10:35','',240,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/240-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(947,1,'2017-01-16 17:10:40','2017-01-16 17:10:40','If you are looking for a reliable and affordable computer repair Cheadle company, why not try e-tec computer services?\r\n\r\nRepairs to systems are undertaken quickly and efficiently, and e-tec computer services, who have over 10 years experience in the computing field, can offer advice with regard to upgrades, software or hardware for your system that may improve overall performance.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nIn addition to computer repair and laptop repair, the following are contained within our portfolio:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Custom built pcs</li>\r\n 	<li>Upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Pc security</li>\r\n 	<li>System health checks</li>\r\n 	<li>Virus removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Servicing</li>\r\n 	<li>Data services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\ne-tec computer services offer a same-day <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">computer repair Cheadle</a> service, on-site, day or night, whenever possible.\r\n\r\nIt is our endeavour to leave customers, old or new, fully satisfied. We believe that once you have used our services, we will always be your first port of call when needing assistance with your laptop or computer.','Computer Repair Cheadle','','inherit','closed','closed','','256-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:40','2017-01-16 17:10:40','',256,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/256-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(948,1,'2017-01-16 17:10:52','2017-01-16 17:10:52','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-920 size-medium\" src=\"http://e-tecpc:8888/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/PC-Case-01-e1293547461909-150x300.gif\" width=\"150\" height=\"300\" />Reliable <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">custom built pcs</a>, quality hardware, awesome prices...</p>\r\n<strong>e-tec computer services</strong> use their knowledge of computing to bring the customer a high quality product, at a lower price than leading competitors.\r\n\r\nWe design and build your system to your exact specification, giving you full control over what goes into your system, thus making it your perfect pc.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nbenefits of a <strong>custom built pc  </strong>\r\n\r\nComputer manufacturers such as Acer, Dell, HP, etc, have come a long way in providing consumers with a number of options for building custom computer systems. Whilst these computers may be adequate for the typical user, you might want a system that can be used for years, after purchase. This being the case, you should definitely consider a custom built computer.\r\n\r\nMost manufacturers use proprietary hardware within their pcs, which can make it extremely difficult to perform upgrades to your system; the various components become obsolete or are not compatible, for example CPUs, RAM, sound and video adapters. Whilst some of these components are upgradable, after the initial purchase, it is often the case that your upgrade options are very limited.\r\n\r\nA <strong>custom built computer</strong> allows you the most flexibility. Taking into consideration the quality of the components used in a custom built system, the cost is often less than buying a pre-built system of the same specifications.\r\n\r\nAnother advantage of a custom built pc is that you are able to start with a very basic system using a low end CPU, perhaps combined with a mid-range system board and minimal memory. You could also start with a system board that has on-board sound and video. Eventually, you may decide to add or upgrade to better components.\r\n\r\nA custom built computer would probably last you a few years before it ‘feels outdated’. At this time, instead of buying a whole new computer you would only need to, at most, swap a few components to make it ‘feel up-to-date’ again.\r\n\r\nWhy Buy From Us?\r\n\r\nWe consider our services to be amongst the most inexpensive in the UK. Not only do we offer incredible prices, but all of our top quality hardware is sourced from reliable and well known suppliers.\r\n\r\nWe DO NOT use cheap components in order to cut down on costs.\r\n\r\nOur systems are built using the best quality hardware together with reliable and high performance components.','Benefits of a Custom Built PC','','inherit','closed','closed','','255-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:52','2017-01-16 17:10:52','',255,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/255-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(949,1,'2017-01-16 17:10:57','2017-01-16 17:10:57','<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-922\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Image-300x231.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"231\" />Solid-state hard drive (SSD)</strong>\r\n\r\nInstalling RAM (random access memory) has always been known as an easy way to boost your system’s performance.\r\n\r\nSSDs (solid state drives) on the other hand, are now much more affordable and a <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">laptop upgrade</a> and <a href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">computer upgrade</a> of your hard drive to an SSD drive has become an even easier way to maximise your computer’s performance.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<strong>benefits of solid state drives</strong>\r\nYou may be wondering why SSDs are all the ‘rage’. What makes them superior?\r\n\r\nThe benefits of a <strong>laptop upgrade</strong> or <strong>computer upgrade</strong> to an SSD are numerous, the major one being the increased performance for ‘read access’, and it is this that interests most people.  Other benefits are listed below:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Unlike traditional hard drives, SSDs have no movable parts and are, therefore, better in handling ‘drops’ and ‘knocks’.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs tend to be more power efficient, and often they can increase the battery life of laptops and netbooks.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs are usually more lightweight than traditional hard drives which in turn mean lighter products.</li>\r\n 	<li>SSDs operate more quietly than traditional hard drives and, because they have no moving parts, generate less heat and tend to have longer life spans.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>performance</strong>\r\nThe areas, in terms of performance, where SSDs really shine are most noticeable when launching applications, booting up and shutting down your computer. A laptop upgrade and computer upgrade to an SSD makes your computer/laptop feel twice as fast when performing these operations.\r\n\r\nA laptop upgrade and computer upgrade to an SSD makes computing an invariably more enjoyable experience, especially if you, like most people, find yourself impatiently tapping your fingers every time the computer starts up or an application loads.\r\n\r\n<strong>Intel’s X-25M Solid-State Drive</strong>\r\n\r\nIntel has spent years perfecting and optimising their SSDs and are definitely one of the leaders in the SSD industry.\r\n\r\nThe Intel X-25M is, in particular, a top-of-the-line SSD in the mobility space.\r\n\r\nAlthough not a first generation device, on paper the Intel X-25M advertises ‘read speeds’ of up to 250 MB/s and ‘write speeds’ up to 70 MB/s.','Solid State Drive Upgrade','','inherit','closed','closed','','254-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:10:57','2017-01-16 17:10:57','',254,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/254-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(950,1,'2017-01-16 17:11:03','2017-01-16 17:11:03','At e-tec computer services we believe in offering a high standard of customer support. Our computer and laptop repair service is competitively priced and we guarantee a fast turnaround time, but this does not mean that we allow price considerations to affect the quality of our repair work. Whether you have software or hardware problems, want to upgrade your computer or laptop, need to recover lost data, e-tec computer services are here to help you.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nOur computer repair technicians are experienced in repair on most major brands of computer and laptop models. We offer computer and laptop repairs for Acer, Dell, Hp, Compaq, Packard bell, Lenovo, Samsung, Toshiba, Sony and many more……\r\n\r\n<strong>Full Range of Computer and Laptop Repair Services:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer Repair Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Blue Screen Repair Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Virus, Spyware, Adware Removal Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Hard Drive Repair Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Data Backup / Recovery</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance / Tune-up / Optimization Service</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop Repair Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop LCD / LED Screen Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Keyboard Repair and Touchpad Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop Power Socket and Adapter Replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Hard Drive / Solid State Drives Upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Memory Upgrades Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Laptop Hinge Repair</li>\r\n 	<li>Motherboard Repair</li>\r\n 	<li>LAN Cable Installation</li>\r\n 	<li>Wireless Network Setup Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Mobile Home or Office Computer / laptop Repair Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>On site Computer Repair &amp; Services in Stalybridge</li>\r\n 	<li>Emergency Computer Repair Call Out Service Stalybridge</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>On Site Repair Service:</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are local, and aim to offer a same-day <a title=\"computer repair Stalybridge\" href=\"http://e-tecpc.co.uk/\" target=\"_self\">computer repair Stalybridge</a> service, on site, day or night, where possible, and will come to your home or office in the Stalybridge area, for free.','PC Repair Stalybridge','','inherit','closed','closed','','253-revision-v1','','','2017-01-16 17:11:03','2017-01-16 17:11:03','',253,'http://e-tecpc:8888/news/253-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(951,1,'2017-01-16 17:11:09','2017-01-16 17:11:09','If you live in the Ashton-Under-Lyne area and are looking for a reliable company for computer repair Ashton, then why not consider e-tec computer services?\r\n\r\nYour pc can start giving you problems for a number of reasons, some of which are detailed below.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>PC fails to boot up</li>\r\n 	<li>Cannot connect to internet</li>\r\n 	<li>Keeps crashing</li>\r\n 	<li>PC very slow and \"clunky\" in use</li>\r\n 	<li>Blue Screen of Death</li>\r\n 	<li>Suspected Virus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\ne-tec computer services, for <a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">computer repair Ashton</a>, can provide a solution by diagnosing and repairing problems as quickly as possible to get you up and running again.\r\n\r\nWe are local, friendly and affordable with over 10 years experience in repairing and upgrading all brands of computers and laptops.\r\n\r\ne-tec computer services aims to build trusting relationships with all of its future customers in <a href=\"http://www.e-tecpc.co.uk/\">computer repair Ashton</a>, and believe that once you experience our services you will never need to go elsewhere.','Computer Repair Ashton','','inherit','closed','closed','','65-revision-v1','','','20